{"word":"G1670 - ἑλκύω - helkýō - hel-koo'-o - Draw","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἑλκύω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">helkýō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hel-koo'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Draw</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - உருவு, இழு"},{"paragraph":"to draw, to attract; to drag"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Probably akin to <a href=\"#/G138 - αἱρέομαι - hairéomai - hahee-reh'-om-ahee/138\">G138</a>; to <i>drag</i> (literally or figuratively): - draw. Compare <a href=\"#/G1667 - ἑλίσσω - helíssō - hel-is'-so/1667\">G1667</a>.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}